Can't believe their prata has gone sub-standard!

Plain one was tough. Egg one didn't fare better -- you'd expect the egg to moisten the texture; but no, it was like an overnight piece!

At much higher price points of $1.70 and $2.70 respectively, there's better value to be found elsewhere (fortunately :)

The only saving grace is perhaps the teh tarik... and the consistently spicy curry lol.

Somehow, Jln Kayu has lost its shine as the preferred prata place; sadly :(

(Still, I remain hopeful that things will turn around... While I seek out other places to makan...)
